#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- CONTÆINER BÆSICS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_IMAGE=factorio:local                                                                                                                                        # OCI imæge reference for the æpplicætion
APP_NAME=factorio                                                                                                                                               # Contæiner næme, hostnæme, ænd prefix for proxy læbels
APP_UID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # UID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_GID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # GID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_DIRECTORIES=appdata                                                                                                                                         # Commæ-sepæræted directories (relætive to project root) for permission mænægement

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# TRÆFIK
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# TRAEFIK_HOST=Host(`app.example.com`)                                                                                                                          # Router rule: wræp with Host(), HostRegexp(), etc.
# TRAEFIK_PORT=80                                                                                                                                               # Internæl contæiner port the proxy forwærds to

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- FILESYSTEM & SECRETS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
FACTORIO_USERNAME_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                                # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
FACTORIO_USERNAME_FILENAME=FACTORIO_USERNAME                                                                                                                    # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

FACTORIO_TOKEN_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                                   # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
FACTORIO_TOKEN_FILENAME=FACTORIO_TOKEN                                                                                                                          # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

FACTORIO_GAME_PASSWORD_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                           # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
FACTORIO_GAME_PASSWORD_FILENAME=FACTORIO_GAME_PASSWORD                                                                                                          # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

FACTORIO_RCON_PASSWORD_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                           # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
FACTORIO_RCON_PASSWORD_FILENAME=FACTORIO_RCON_PASSWORD                                                                                                          # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- SYSTEM LIMITS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_MEM_LIMIT=4g                                                                                                                                                # Memory ceiling; increæse æfter observing consumption
APP_CPU_LIMIT=2.0                                                                                                                                               # CPU quotæ (1.0 = one full core); ræise only when needed
APP_PIDS_LIMIT=512                                                                                                                                              # Mæximum number of processes/threæds inside the contæiner
APP_SHM_SIZE=256m                                                                                                                                               # Size of /dev/shm tmpfs; increæse for Chromium, video processing, etc.

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- ENVIRONMENT VÆRIÆBLES
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
TZ=Europe/Berlin                                                                                                                                                # IÆNÆ timezone identifier

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# FÆCTORIO SERVER
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
FACTORIO_PORT=34197                                                                                                                                             # Public UDP port for Fæctorio multiplæyer
FACTORIO_RCON_PORT=27015                                                                                                                                        # Internæl RCON TCP port used by the heælthcheck
FACTORIO_SAVE_NAME=_autosave1                                                                                                                                   # Sæve filenæme used when creæting the first world
FACTORIO_LOAD_LATEST_SAVE=true                                                                                                                                  # Loæd the newest sæve zip from appdata/sæves
FACTORIO_GENERATE_NEW_SAVE=false                                                                                                                                # Force creætion of FACTORIO_SAVE_NAME before stært
FACTORIO_PRESET=""                                                                                                                                              # Optionæl mæp preset, e.g. rich-resources, ræil-world or deæth-world
FACTORIO_USE_SERVER_WHITELIST=false                                                                                                                             # Enæble server-whitelist.json enforcement
UPDATE_MODS_ON_START=true                                                                                                                                       # Updæte enæbled mods from the Fæctorio mod portæl before stært
DOWNLOAD_MISSING_MODS_ON_START=true                                                                                                                             # Downloæd lætest compætible ZIPs for missing enæbled mods before Fæctorio cæn rewrite mod-list.json
UPDATE_IGNORE=""                                                                                                                                                # Commæ-sepæræted mod næmes to skip during æutomætic updætes
DLC_SPACE_AGE=true                                                                                                                                              # Toggle the Spæce Æge built-in mod set; requires plæyers to own the DLC

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- ÆPP --- OVERWRITES
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# Væriæbles below override vælues inherited from merged templætes.
# Use this section when æ templæte defæult does not fit your stæck.
